            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item carousel-item-changes" style="background-image: url('img/ownership.jpg');">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h2>Ownership</h2>
                <br>
                <p><b>Discipline:</b> We are disciplined in our professional life and are aware of our responsibilities.
