                </p>
                <p><b>Progressive:</b> Have a progressive, positive and open mindset towards changes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item carousel-item-changes" style="background-image: url('img/empathy.jpg');">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h2>Empathy</h2>
                <br>
                <p><b>Family culture:</b> Practice Indian family culture by being respectful and fair to each other. Value, recognize and develop our team by providing equal opportunity to all.
                </p>
                <p><b>Respect Environment:</b> Ensure that we follow the laid out health, safety & environment policy while conducting our business.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    function changeSlide(index) {
        var carousel = new bootstrap.Carousel(document.getElementById('coreCarousel'));
        carousel.to(index);
        
        let divs = document.querySelectorAll('.core-containers');
        divs.forEach(div => {
            div.style.backgroundColor = '';
            div.style.color = '';
        });

        divs[index].style.backgroundColor = '#007bff';
        divs[index].style.color = 'white';
    }
</script>
<!-- Core result end -->
 
